    {
      "id": "el_23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 797,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P=5000, R=8%, T=3 years\nStep 2: SI = P×R×T / 100\n  = 5000 × 8 × 3 / 100 = 1200\n  Yr1: +400 | Yr2: +400 | Yr3: +400\n\nTRICK:\n8% of 5000 = 400/yr × 3 = 1200\n(find 1yr interest, multiply by T)\n\n  P=5000 ──[8%×3yr]──→ SI=1200\n  Amount = 5000 + 1200 = 6200\n\nAnswer: SI = Rs.1200 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
