    {
      "id": "el_28",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 797,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI=600, R=10%, T=2 years\nStep 2: P = 100×SI / (R×T)\n  = 100×600 / (10×2) = 3000\n\nTRICK:\n10% for 2yr = 20% total SI\nSI=600 is 20% of P → P = 600×100/20\n= 3000\n\n  P=? ──[10%×2yr]──→ SI=600\n  Verify: 3000×10×2/100 = 600 ✓\n\nAnswer: P = Rs.3000 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 28,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI=600, R=10%, T=2 years\nStep 2: P = 100×SI / (R×T)\n  = 100×600 / (10×2) = 3000\n\nTRICK:\n10% for 2yr = 20% total SI\nSI=600 is 20% of P → P = 600×100/20\n= 3000\n\n  P=? ──[10%×2yr]──→ SI=600\n  Verify: 3000×10×2/100 = 600 ✓\n\nAnswer: P = Rs.3000 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
