      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 732,
      "width": 758,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "A principal of Rs.800 amounts to Rs.920 in 3 years at\nsimple interest. Find the rate of interest per annum.",
      "fontSize": 13,
