    },
    {
      "id": "el_33",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 797,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI = 920-800 = 120, T=3\nStep 2: R = 100×SI/(P×T)\n  = 100×120/(800×3) = 5%\n\nTRICK:\nSI/yr = 120/3 = 40\nR = (40/800)×100 = 5%\n(yearly interest as % of principal)\n\n  |████████████████|░░░| Rs.920\n  |◄── P=800 ────►|120|\n\nAnswer: R = 5% per annum ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 33,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI = 920-800 = 120, T=3\nStep 2: R = 100×SI/(P×T)\n  = 100×120/(800×3) = 5%\n\nTRICK:\nSI/yr = 120/3 = 40\nR = (40/800)×100 = 5%\n(yearly interest as % of principal)\n\n  |████████████████|░░░| Rs.920\n  |◄── P=800 ────►|120|\n\nAnswer: R = 5% per annum ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
