    {
      "id": "el_38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1165,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P=1500, SI=450, R=6%\nStep 2: T = 100×SI/(P×R)\n  = 100×450/(1500×6) = 5\n\nTRICK:\nSI/yr = 1500×6/100 = 90\nT = 450/90 = 5 years\n\n  |--Yr1--|--Yr2--|--Yr3--|--Yr4--|--Yr5--|\n  | +90   | +90   | +90   | +90   | +90  |\n  |◄────────── SI = 450 ──────────────►|\n\nAnswer: T = 5 years ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
