      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P=1500, SI=450, R=6%\nStep 2: T = 100×SI/(P×R)\n  = 100×450/(1500×6) = 5\n\nTRICK:\nSI/yr = 1500×6/100 = 90\nT = 450/90 = 5 years\n\n  |--Yr1--|--Yr2--|--Yr3--|--Yr4--|--Yr5--|\n  | +90   | +90   | +90   | +90   | +90  |\n  |◄────────── SI = 450 ──────────────►|\n\nAnswer: T = 5 years ✓",
