    {
      "id": "el_43",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1165,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P=12000, R=9%, T=4\nStep 2: SI = 12000×9×4/100 = 4320\nStep 3: A = 12000+4320 = 16320\n\nTRICK:\nA = P(1 + RT/100)\n= 12000(1 + 36/100) = 12000×1.36\n= 16320\n\n  |██████████████|░░░░░░| Amount\n  |◄── P=12000 ─►|SI=4320|\n  |◄──── A = 16320 ────►|\n\nAnswer: Amount = Rs.16320 ✓",
