    {
      "id": "el_48",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1149,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Doubles → SI = P\n  P×R×8/100 = P → R×8 = 100\nStep 2: R = 100/8 = 12.5%\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: R×T = (N-1)×100\n2× → R = 100/T = 100/8 = 12.5%\n3× → R = 200/T | N× → (N-1)×100/T\n\n  |████████████|░░░░░░░░░░| 2P\n  |◄── P ─────►|◄─ SI=P ─►|\n\nAnswer: R = 12.5% per annum ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 48,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
