        "type_6"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Doubles → SI = P\n  P×R×8/100 = P → R×8 = 100\nStep 2: R = 100/8 = 12.5%\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: R×T = (N-1)×100\n2× → R = 100/T = 100/8 = 12.5%\n3× → R = 200/T | N× → (N-1)×100/T\n\n  |████████████|░░░░░░░░░░| 2P\n  |◄── P ─────►|◄─ SI=P ─►|\n\nAnswer: R = 12.5% per annum ✓",
