      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1547,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 5 times → SI = 4P\n  P×R×12/100 = 4P → R×12 = 400\nStep 2: R = 400/12 = 33 1/3 %\n\nTRICK:\nFormula: R = (N-1)×100/T\n= (5-1)×100/12 = 400/12 = 33 1/3 %\n\n  |██|░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░| 5P\n  |P |◄── SI = 4P ───►|\n\nAnswer: R = 33 1/3 % per annum ✓",
