    {
      "id": "el_58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1547,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI1 = 2000×8×3/100 = 480\n  SI2 = 2000×6×3/100 = 360\nStep 2: Diff = 480-360 = 120\n\nTRICK:\nDiff = P×T×(R1-R2)/100\n= 2000×3×2/100 = 120\n\n  At 8%: |████████████████████| 480\n  At 6%: |███████████████|      360\n         |               |░░░░| 120\n\nAnswer: Diff = Rs.120 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
