      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI1 = 2000×8×3/100 = 480\n  SI2 = 2000×6×3/100 = 360\nStep 2: Diff = 480-360 = 120\n\nTRICK:\nDiff = P×T×(R1-R2)/100\n= 2000×3×2/100 = 120\n\n  At 8%: |████████████████████| 480\n  At 6%: |███████████████|      360\n         |               |░░░░| 120\n\nAnswer: Diff = Rs.120 ✓",
