    {
      "id": "el_63",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1563,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: x at 5%, (4000-x) at 9%\n  5x/100 + 9(4000-x)/100 = 220\nStep 2: 5x+36000-9x = 22000\n  -4x = -14000 → x = 3500\n\nTRICK:\nAvg rate = 220×100/4000 = 5.5%\nAlligation: (9-5.5):(5.5-5) = 7:1\nParts = 4000×7/8 : 4000×1/8 = 3500:500\n\n  |◄─ 3500@5% ─►|◄ 500@9% ►|\n\nAnswer: Rs.3500 and Rs.500 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6300,
