      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: x at 5%, (4000-x) at 9%\n  5x/100 + 9(4000-x)/100 = 220\nStep 2: 5x+36000-9x = 22000\n  -4x = -14000 → x = 3500\n\nTRICK:\nAvg rate = 220×100/4000 = 5.5%\nAlligation: (9-5.5):(5.5-5) = 7:1\nParts = 4000×7/8 : 4000×1/8 = 3500:500\n\n  |◄─ 3500@5% ─►|◄ 500@9% ►|\n\nAnswer: Rs.3500 and Rs.500 ✓",
