      "id": "el_83",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2315,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Pays = 5000×4/100 = 200/yr\n  Earns = 5000×6/100 = 300/yr\nStep 2: Gain = 300-200 = 100/yr\n\nTRICK:\nGain = P × (Lend%-Borrow%) / 100\n= 5000 × (6-4)/100 = 100/yr\n\n  Borrows@4%: ──→ Pays Rs.200/yr\n  Lends@6%:   ◄── Gets Rs.300/yr\n  Net Gain = Rs.100/yr\n\nAnswer: Gain = Rs.100 per year ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8300,
      "version": 1,
