    },
    {
      "id": "el_88",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2331,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI(3yr) = 2800-2200 = 600\n  SI/yr = 200, SI(2yr) = 400\nStep 2: P = 2200-400 = 1800\n  R = 100×400/(1800×2) = 11 1/9 %\n\nTRICK:\nSI/yr = (A2-A1)/(T2-T1)\n= 600/3 = 200\nP = A1 - SI/yr×T1 = 2200-400 = 1800\n\n  P=1800──→2200(2yr)──→2800(5yr)\n\nAnswer: P = Rs.1800, R = 11 1/9 % ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 88,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
