      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SI(3yr) = 2800-2200 = 600\n  SI/yr = 200, SI(2yr) = 400\nStep 2: P = 2200-400 = 1800\n  R = 100×400/(1800×2) = 11 1/9 %\n\nTRICK:\nSI/yr = (A2-A1)/(T2-T1)\n= 600/3 = 200\nP = A1 - SI/yr×T1 = 2200-400 = 1800\n\n  P=1800──→2200(2yr)──→2800(5yr)\n\nAnswer: P = Rs.1800, R = 11 1/9 % ✓",
